        "timestamp": "2021-06-23 18:04:09.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nCan you please test this in the sandbox? I am not sure if the parameter gets passed since this variable is not defined in the original global-jjb template. If it does not work, then we will need to add it in global-jjb first.",
        "patchset_number": 1
